es to make life and mobility easierwe are testing the thesis of satisfying demand and make money at it fields said from san francisco the concept is that making peoples lives better is good business and if decades from now the world is buying fewer vehicles ford wants to have a big slice of that smaller pierelated fords next step to making autonomous driving a realitybuy photo photo detroit free pressas the automaker takes research projects into autonomous driving and starts to implement them ford is also piloting some car sharing programs ceo mark fields announced in a speech at the automakers research and innovation center in palo alto tuesdayit is part of the larger ford smart mobility plan that incorporates connectivity mobility autonomous vehicles and big data ford introduced the plan in january along with  experiments aimed at better understanding consumers mobility needs around the globemy greatgrandfather helped put the world on wheels so everyone could enjoy the benefits of mobility said ford executive chairman bill ford in a statement our vision today is to expand that same thinking using advanced technology and new business models and addressing the mobility challenges people face around the worldafter gathering data and consumer insights for six months ford is using that data to proceed in two areas car sharing and alternative ways of getting around increasingly congested cities where many forms of transportation share the roadford motor credit will team with two carsharing companies getaround in the us and easycar club in london the idea is a customer can rent a car that was financed through ford credit to prescreened clientsthe peerpeer car sharing pilot program will run through november and involve  customers in six us cities who will use getaround software it will be offered to customers in berkeley oakland and san francisco in california as well as in portland oregon chicago and washington dc it runs through novemberrelated mark fields earns m in first year as ford ceobuy photo photo alisa priddle detroit free pressfields is hoping the program will make ford owners more loyal customers and expose those who dont own a car to what ford has to offer for when they are in the marketit will raise awareness and is a bridge to ownership fields saidanother  ford owners in london will use easycar club to rent out their car it is a way to offset monthly paymentsconsumers tell us they are interested in sharing the costs of vehicle ownership and this program will help us understand how much that extends to customers who are financing a ford vehicle said david mcclelland ford credit vice president of marketing as most vehicles are parked and out of use much of the time this can help us gauge our customers desires to pick up extra cash and keep their vehicles in usea third of millennials are interested in renting out their own belongings to supplement their income according to independent researchers penn schoen berland and they say after lending a book a car is the item they are most open to sharing and half are open to the ideahalf of millennial and generation z consumers say they would share a car for the cost savings  say it is a good way to try a new productbuy photo photo alisa priddledetroit free pressand ford will participate in an uberlike model with godrive an ondemand car sharing pilot in london where you order a car and pay for a oneway trip with guaranteed parking there will be  cars positioned in 0 locations available for payasyougo perminute pricing in cars such as the focus electric caras part of the research into how people get around today ford is introducing a new electric bike concept modeflex and an extension of the modelink prototype smartphone app to use the ebike the app provides realtime information on weather congestion parking costs time traffic and public transportation as well as navigation route planning and health and fitness informationthere is even a version of the app for the smartwatchfields did not rule out making ebikes in the future if the research suggests that is a viable business to pursuewe now are moving from experimentation to implementation said fields we have learned a lot in the past six months and now are ready to put insights into action our goal is to make peoples lives better by helping them more easily navigate through their day address societal issues and over time change the way the world moves – just as henry ford did more than 0 years agocontact alisa priddle 54 or apriddlefreepresscom follow her on twitter alisapriddle 37 connecttweet 4 linkedin  commentemailmoreread or share this story httponfreepcomnkggr aerosol paint menu  75 no items in cart products field markers stencils paintchalk aerosol paint aerosol chalk bulk paint bulk chalk tarpsscreenscovers sandbags marking tools accessoriesparts products ecommerce productcategory list aerosol paint ameristripe paint  item 05 view details durastripe paint 5 item 070 view details ecostripe paint 4 item 3 view details breast cancer awareness stencil and paint package 555 item  view details product   of  trumark athletics sports field paint menu  75 no items in cart products field markers stencils paintchalk aerosol paint aerosol chalk bulk paint bulk chalk tarpsscreenscovers sandbags marking tools accessoriesparts products ecommerce productcategory list paintchalk play inspired your field shouldn’t just look good it should inspire your performance whether you’re playing under the lights on tv or grinding it out in practice we have the right paint to help your team make a splash in front of fans alumni recruits and recruiters pick the paint that’s right for you need help picking a paint brand or color learn more about paints on our faq page or contact us now for help picking paint that meets your needs aerosol paint view products bulk paint view products aerosol chalk view products bulk chalk view products